OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1774210270
OL,3,CPM to chair Cobra meeting as Iran war
OL,4,Cthreatens cost of living crisis
OL,6,FThe prime minister is due to chair a
OL,7,Fmeeting of the government's emergency
OL,8,FCobra committee to discuss the
OL,9,Feconomic impact of the Iran war, ITV
OL,10,FNews understands.
OL,12,FMonday's meeting will focus on the
OL,13,Fcost of living, something that is seen
OL,14,Fas a top priority by senior ministers,
OL,15,Fincluding the foreign secretary.
OL,17,FBank of England Governor Andrew Bailey
OL,18,Fis expected to attend.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
